OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fvariable cloud throughout the day.
OL,7,FMostly dry but the odd light shower
OL,8,Fpossible. Southwest winds will freshen
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some hazy sunshine
OL,12,Fin the evening. Cloudy with showery
OL,13,Frain for Shetland overnight. Staying
OL,14,Fdry but largely cloudy for Orkney.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FCloudy throughout the day
OL,17,Ffor Shetland with showery outbreaks of
OL,18,Frain. Largely cloudy and mostly dry
OL,19,Ffor Orkney with the chance of the odd
OL,20,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
